alg.description: The algorithm to use. Should be one of 'EdDSA', 'ES256', 'ES384', 'ES512', 'RS256' (default), 'RS384', 'RS512', 'PS256', 'PS384', 'PS512'  for verification or one of 'RSA1_5', 'RSA-OAEP', 'RSA-OAEP-256', 'ECDH-ES', 'ECDH-ES+A128KW', 'ECDH-ES+A192KW', 'ECDH-ES+A256KW' for encryption.

size.description: Key size in bits (e.g. 2048 if generating an RSA key). Default is 4096

use.description: Desired public key usage (use header), one of [enc sig]. Defaults to 'sig'

block.description: The resource `jose` generates a JWKS keypair
